British Land Co Plc &lt;BLND.L> convertibleeurobond issued yesterday has been raised to a total of 33 mlnstg from the 30 mln originally indicated, lead manager CreditSuisse First Boston Ltd said.    The coupon has been fixed at 7.50 pct and the conversionprice at 248 pence to give a 27.84 pct premium over lastnight's share price close on the London stock exchange. REUTER&#3;